Sentencas: The current study examined the effect of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF) and La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 (LSM) coatings on the electrical properties and oxidation resistance of Crofer22 APU at 800 degrees C hot air.
Titulo: High temperature oxidation behavior of interconnect coated with LSCF and LSM for solid oxide fuel cell by screen printing

Sentencas: LSCF and LSM were coated on Crofer22 APU by screen printing and sintered over temperatures ranging from 1000 to 1100 degrees C in N-2.
Titulo: High temperature oxidation behavior of interconnect coated with LSCF and LSM for solid oxide fuel cell by screen printing

Sentencas: The coated alloy was first checked for compositions, morphology and interface conditions and then treated in a simulated oxidizing environment at 800 degrees C for 200 h. After measuring the long-term electrical resistance, the area specific resistance (ASR) at 800 degrees C for the alloy coated with LSCF was less than its counterpart coated with LSM.
Titulo: High temperature oxidation behavior of interconnect coated with LSCF and LSM for solid oxide fuel cell by screen printing

Sentencas: This work used LSCF coating as a metallic interconnect to reduce working temperature for the solid oxide fuel cell.
Titulo: High temperature oxidation behavior of interconnect coated with LSCF and LSM for solid oxide fuel cell by screen printing
